    "excerpt": "A heartfelt Christmas and New Year message from CEO Saffa Andrew Koroma to the CArCRT team, celebrating dedication, unity, and hope.",
    "content": "Dear Team,\nAs we celebrate this joyful season, I want to take a moment to express my heartfelt gratitude to each of you. Your dedication, resilience, and teamwork throughout the year have been the driving force behind our successes and the impact we continue to make in our communities.\nChristmas reminds us of the power of hope, unity, and generosity. These values are at the core of our mission, and I am proud to see them reflected in the way you serve, support, and inspire others every day.\nMay this festive season bring peace, joy, and renewal to you and your families. As we step into the new year, let us carry forward the spirit of collaboration and excellence, knowing that together we can achieve even greater milestones.\nThank you for your commitment and for being an integral part of this journey.\nWishing you all a Merry Christmas and a prosperous New Year filled with blessings and opportunities.\n\nSAFFA ANDREW KOROMA\nChief Executive Officer.",
